It was a simulation.

08:44.208 --> 08:47.000
Give them a chance, Heatwave.

08:44.208 --> 08:47.000
They've have been studying.

08:47.041 --> 08:49.208
Right, guys?

08:49.250 --> 08:51.041
And we'll keep an eye

08:49.250 --> 08:51.041
