What?

10:11.667 --> 10:13.208
We're supposed to consider

10:13.250 --> 10:15.000
people's safety first.

10:15.041 --> 10:16.542
Everybody else

10:15.041 --> 10:16.542
was standing around yakking.

10:16.583 --> 10:18.208
I took action.

10:18.250 --> 10:19.625
Isn't that what

10:18.250 --> 10:19.625
