10:19.667 --> 10:22.208
COMPUTERIZED VOICE:

10:19.667 --> 10:22.208
Going up. Going up.

10:22.250 --> 10:24.375
Going...

10:24.417 --> 10:26.291
( sighs )

10:29.000 --> 10:31.417
Never know.

10:29.000 --> 10:31.417
Might come in handy.

10:34.083 --> 10:38.041
Blurr, you put one

10:34.083 --> 10:38.041
