10:38.083 --> 10:41.458
It won't happen again, Chief.

10:38.083 --> 10:41.458
I'll make sure.

10:41.500 --> 10:42.667
Why do we even bother?

10:42.709 --> 10:44.583
All humans do

10:42.709 --> 10:44.583
