10:48.083 --> 10:49.625
We're here for a reason.

10:49.667 --> 10:52.041
Autobots and humans

10:49.667 --> 10:52.041
share a common destiny,

10:52.083 --> 10:53.959
and have for centuries.

10:54.000 --> 10:56.750
We should know that

10:54.000 --> 10:56.750
better than anybody.

10:56.792 --> 10:58.750
Maybe if you learned

10:56.792 --> 10:58.750
more about humans,

10:58.792 --> 11:00.333
you'd like them better.

11:00.375 --> 11:02.250
They're actually

11:00.375 --> 11:02.250
pretty fascinating.

11:02.291 --> 11:03.583
I'll tell you one thing.

11:03.625 --> 11:05.000
You couldn't ask

11:03.625 --> 11:05.000
for better partners

11:05.041 --> 11:06.542
than the Burns Family.

11:06.583 --> 11:08.583
They're as loyal as any Bots

11:06.583 --> 11:08.583
I've ever known.

11:08.625 --> 11:11.125
Filed under T for "Teamwork."

11:13.125 --> 11:15.125
I'll understand if you don't

11:13.125 --> 11:15.125
want to be part of this mission.

11:15.166 --> 11:18.458
It's dangerous, and Griffin Rock

11:15.166 --> 11:18.458
isn't your home.

11:18.500 --> 11:20.208
Wherever there is

11:18.500 --> 11:20.208
