11:20.250 --> 11:23.291
there are Rescue Bots ready

11:20.250 --> 11:23.291
to serve, save, and protect.

11:23.333 --> 11:26.083
We didn't have the chance

11:23.333 --> 11:26.083
to save our home.

11:26.125 --> 11:28.083
We won't let you

11:26.125 --> 11:28.083
lose yours.

11:28.125 --> 11:30.125
The lava's moving too fast.

11:30.166 --> 11:32.250
( rocks crumbling )

11:32.291 --> 11:34.625
Good a place as any

11:32.291 --> 11:34.625
