11:42.166 --> 11:43.625
BLADES:

11:42.166 --> 11:43.625
I can't see.

11:43.667 --> 11:45.625
Aah!

11:43.667 --> 11:45.625
I'll guide you.

11:45.667 --> 11:48.583
You're right-side up.

11:45.667 --> 11:48.583
Just take us as high as you can.

11:48.625 --> 11:50.250
It's okay if you go slow.

11:50.291 --> 11:51.667
Here goes nothing.

11:55.375 --> 12:00.375
We saved everyone.

11:55.375 --> 12:00.375
This is high-five time.

12:02.750 --> 12:04.333
No one?

12:06.667 --> 12:08.208
All right,

12:06.667 --> 12:08.208
I have a question.

12:08.250 --> 12:11.458
Dani. She's different

12:08.250 --> 12:11.458
