12:22.875 --> 12:24.500
Ah, yes, the mustache.

12:24.542 --> 12:26.709
It appears to be a point

12:24.542 --> 12:26.709
of pride with some people,

12:26.750 --> 12:28.333
like Chief.

12:28.375 --> 12:29.750
We don't know exactly

12:28.375 --> 12:29.750
how it works,

12:29.792 --> 12:32.667
